":doc:`Product variants </applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/"
"variants>` are different versions of the same product, created by "
"combining :ref:`attributes <products/variants/attributes>` like color, size, "
"material, etc., which can lead to differences in price and/or availability."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Productvarianten </applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/"
"variants>` zijn verschillende versies van hetzelfde product, gecreëerd "
"door :ref:`kenmerken <products/variants/attributes>` zoals kleur, maat, "
"materiaal, enz. te combineren, wat kan leiden tot verschillen in prijs en/of "
"beschikbaarheid."

