"naar :menuselection:`Website --> E-commerce --> Orders` te gaan en de "
"filter :guilabel:`Bevestigd` te verwijderen. Open vervolgens het :icon:`fa-"
"caret-down` vervolgkeuzemenu en selecteer onder :guilabel:`Filters` de "
"optie :guilabel:`Onbetaald`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:42
msgid ""
"E-commerce orders can be automatically assigned to a specific sales team or "
"salesperson. To do so, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`. In the :guilabel:`eCommerce` section, under :guilabel:`Orders "
"Assignment`, select the relevant :guilabel:`Sales Team` "
"or :guilabel:`Salesperson`."
msgstr ""
"E-commerceorders kunnen automatisch worden toegewezen aan een specifiek "
"verkoopteam of verkoper. Ga naar :menuselection:`Website --> Configuratie --"
"> Instellingen`. Selecteer in het gedeelte :guilabel:`E-commerce` "
"onder :guilabel:`Ordertoewijzing` het relevante :guilabel:`Verkoopteam` of "
"de relevante :guilabel:`Verkoper`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:48
msgid ""
"This three-step process is not visible to customers. However, they can view "
"their orders and check their status through the customer :doc:`portal </"
"applications/general/users/user_portals>`."
msgstr ""
"Dit proces van drie stappen is niet zichtbaar voor klanten. Ze kunnen hun "
"orders wel bekijken en de status controleren via het klant:doc:`portaal </"
"applications/general/users/user_portals>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:51
msgid ""
"If the customer pays via :ref:`wire transfer <payment_providers/"
"bank_payments/wire_transfer>`, the quotation is *not* automatically "
"confirmed. In this case, the customer receives a notification on "
"the :guilabel:`My account` page of their :doc:`customer account "
"<configuration/customer_accounts>` to review and pay for the order. After "
"the payment is received, the order must be manually confirmed in the backend."
msgstr ""
"Als de klant betaalt via :ref:`bankoverschrijving <payment_providers/"
"bank_payments/wire_transfer>`, wordt de offerte *niet* automatisch "
"bevestigd. In dit geval ontvangt de klant een melding op de "
"pagina :guilabel:`Mijn account` van hun :doc:`klantaccount <configuration/"
"customer_accounts>` om de bestelling te bekijken en te betalen. Nadat de "
"betaling is ontvangen, moet de bestelling handmatig worden bevestigd in de "
"backend."

