#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:19
msgid ""
"The eCommerce reporting view allows you to monitor and analyze the "
"performance of your online sales. To access it, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Reporting --> eCommerce`. "
"The :guilabel:`eCommerce Dashboard` helps monitor everything related to the "
"online shop, e.g., sales performance by product or category. By default, the "
"graph shows data for :guilabel:`Confirmed Orders` and the current month."
msgstr ""
"De e-commerce rapportageweergave stelt je in staat de prestaties van je "
"online verkoop te monitoren en analyseren. Ga naar :menuselection:`Website --"
"> Rapportage --> E-commerce` om deze te openen. Het :guilabel:`E-commerce "
"dashboard` helpt bij het monitoren van alles wat gerelateerd is aan de "
"online winkel, bv. verkoopprestaties per product of categorie. Standaard "
"toont de grafiek gegevens voor :guilabel:`Bevestigde orders` en de huidige "
"maand."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:25
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Measures` :icon:`fa-caret-down` button to select the "
"metric to analyze, such as :guilabel:`Discount %`, :guilabel:`Qty "
"Invoiced`, :guilabel:`Untaxed Total` (default), or :guilabel:`Volume`. You "
"can also switch between :ref:`pivot <studio/views/reporting/pivot>` "
"and :ref:`graph <studio/views/reporting/graph>` views, and create a "
"spreadsheet by clicking :guilabel:`Insert in Spreadsheet`."
msgstr ""
"Klik op de knop :guilabel:`Meetwaarden` :icon:`fa-caret-down` om de te "
"analyseren metriek te selecteren, zoals :guilabel:`Korting "
"%`, :guilabel:`Gefactureerde hoeveelheid`, :guilabel:`Totaal exclusief btw` "
"(standaard) of :guilabel:`Volume`. Je kunt ook schakelen "
"tussen :ref:`draaitabel <studio/views/reporting/pivot>`- en :ref:`grafiek "
"<studio/views/reporting/graph>`weergaven, en een spreadsheet maken door "
"op :guilabel:`Invoegen in spreadsheet` te klikken."

