msgstr "Schakel de :ref:`developer-mode` in."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:55
msgid ""
"Open the Settings app and go to :menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> "
"System Parameters`."
msgstr ""
"Open de app Instellingen en ga naar :menuselection:`Instellingen --> "
"Technisch --> Systeemparameters`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:56
msgid ""
"Search for the :guilabel:`sale.async_emails` system parameter, set "
"its :guilabel:`Value` to `True`, and click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Zoek naar de systeemparameter :guilabel:`sale.async_emails`, stel "
"de :guilabel:`Waarde` in op `True` en klik op :guilabel:`Opslaan`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:58
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> Scheduled Actions`."
msgstr ""
"Ga naar :menuselection:`Instellingen --> Technisch --> Geplande acties`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:59
msgid "Select the :guilabel:`Sales: Send pending emails` scheduled action."
msgstr ""
"Selecteer de geplande actie :guilabel:`Verkoop: Verstuur openstaande e-"
"mails`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:60
msgid "Ensure the :guilabel:`Active` switch is enabled."
msgstr "Zorg ervoor dat de schakelaar :guilabel:`Actief` is ingeschakeld."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:63
msgid ""
"This configuration is recommended only for high-traffic websites, as it may "
"introduce unnecessary delays for order confirmation and invoice emails on "
"websites with moderate traffic."
msgstr ""
"Deze configuratie wordt alleen aanbevolen voor websites met veel verkeer, "
"omdat het onnodige vertragingen kan veroorzaken voor orderbevestigings- en "
"factuure-mails op websites met gemiddeld verkeer."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:3
msgid "Delivery methods"
msgstr "Leveringsmethoden"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo eCommerce allows you to configure various delivery methods, enabling "
"customers to choose their preferred option at :ref:`checkout <ecommerce/"
"checkout/steps>`. These methods include integrations with :ref:`external "
"providers <ecommerce/shipping/external-provider>` as well as :ref:`custom "
"options <ecommerce/shipping/custom-method>` such as flat-rate shipping, free "
"shipping, or :ref:`in-store pickup <ecommerce/shipping/instore-pickup>`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo E-commerce stelt je in staat om verschillende leveringsmethoden te "
"configureren, zodat klanten bij het :ref:`afrekenen <ecommerce/checkout/"
"steps>` hun voorkeursoptie kunnen kiezen. Deze methoden omvatten integraties "
"met :ref:`externe providers <ecommerce/shipping/external-provider>` "
"en :ref:`aangepaste opties <ecommerce/shipping/custom-method>` zoals "
"verzending tegen een vast tarief, gratis verzending of :ref:`afhalen in "
"winkel <ecommerce/shipping/instore-pickup>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:12
msgid ""
":doc:`Configuring delivery methods </applications/inventory_and_mrp/"
"inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Leveringsmethoden configureren </applications/inventory_and_mrp/"
"inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:18
msgid "External provider integration"
msgstr "Externe provider-integratie"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:20
msgid ""
"You can integrate with :doc:`third-party shipping carriers </applications/"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/"
"third_party_shipper>`, such as :doc:`FedEx </applications/inventory_and_mrp/"
"inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex>`, :doc:`UPS </"
"applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/ups_credentials>`, or :doc:`DHL </applications/"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/"
"dhl_credentials>` to streamline shipping operations. Connecting with an "
"external provider allows to generate :doc:`tracking labels </applications/"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels>` "
"automatically and to offer customers several delivery options "
"at :ref:`checkout <ecommerce/checkout/steps>`."
msgstr ""
"Je kunt integreren met :doc:`externe vervoerders </applications/"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/"
"third_party_shipper>`, zoals :doc:`FedEx </applications/inventory_and_mrp/"
"inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex>`, :doc:`UPS </"
"applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/ups_credentials>` of :doc:`DHL </applications/"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/"
"dhl_credentials>` om verzendactiviteiten te stroomlijnen. Verbinding maken "
"met een externe provider maakt het mogelijk om "
"automatisch :doc:`trackinglabels </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels>` te genereren en klanten "
"verschillende leveringsopties aan te bieden bij het :ref:`afrekenen "
"<ecommerce/checkout/steps>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:31
msgid "To enable a third-party delivery provider:"
msgstr "Om een externe bezorgdienst in te schakelen:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:34
msgid "Scroll to the :guilabel:`eCommerce` section."
msgstr "Scroll naar de sectie :guilabel:`E-commerce`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:35
msgid ""
"Under :guilabel:`Configure Delivery Methods`, click :icon:`fa-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`Find a Delivery Provider`."
msgstr ""
"Klik onder :guilabel:`Leveringsmethoden configureren` op :icon:`fa-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`Zoek een bezorgdienst`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:37
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`New Providers` page, click the :guilabel:`Delivery "
"methods` button of an already-installed provider to access the delivery "
"method's form, or :guilabel:`Install` a new provider."
msgstr ""
"Klik op de pagina :guilabel:`Nieuwe providers` op de "
"knop :guilabel:`Leveringsmethoden` van een reeds geïnstalleerde provider om "
"toegang te krijgen tot het formulier van de leveringsmethode, "
"of :guilabel:`Installeer` een nieuwe provider."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:40
msgid ""
":doc:`Configure the delivery method </applications/inventory_and_mrp/"
"inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper>`."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Configureer de leveringsmethode </applications/inventory_and_mrp/"
