#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:44
msgid ""
"The :ref:`shipping price <inventory/shipping/calculate-delivery-cost>`, "
"including the :guilabel:`Margin on rate` or :guilabel:`Additional margin` "
"configured on the :ref:`delivery method <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"configure-delivery-method>` (if applicable), is displayed when selecting the "
"provider during :ref:`checkout <ecommerce/checkout/steps>`."
msgstr ""
"De :ref:`verzendprijs <inventory/shipping/calculate-delivery-cost>`, "
"inclusief de :guilabel:`Marge op tarief` of :guilabel:`Aanvullende marge` "
"geconfigureerd op de :ref:`leveringsmethode <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"configure-delivery-method>` (indien van toepassing), wordt weergegeven bij "
"het selecteren van de provider tijdens het :ref:`afrekenen <ecommerce/"
"checkout/steps>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:50
msgid ""
"It is also possible to connect your e-commerce to shipping aggregators, such "
"as :doc:`Sendcloud </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping>` "
"or :doc:`Envia.com </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping>`, or to fulfillment "
"platforms like :doc:`Gelato </applications/sales/sales/gelato>`."
msgstr ""
"Het is ook mogelijk om je e-commerce te verbinden met verzendaggregators, "
"zoals :doc:`Sendcloud </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping>` "
"of :doc:`Envia.com </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping>`, of met fulfillment-"
"platforms zoals :doc:`Gelato </applications/sales/sales/gelato>`."

