"All pages using the :guilabel:`Form`, :guilabel:`Newsletter Block`, "
"or :guilabel:`Newsletter Popup` snippets are protected by both tools. Web "
"login, sign-up and password reset pages are also protected."
msgstr ""
"Alle pagina's die de "
"fragmenten :guilabel:`Formulier`, :guilabel:`Nieuwsbriefblok` "
"of :guilabel:`Nieuwsbriefpop-up` gebruiken, worden door beide tools "
"beschermd. Webinlog-, registratie- en wachtwoordherstelpagina's worden ook "
"beschermd."

