"personaliseren, waaronder :ref:`alinea's en koppen <website/themes/"
"paragraphs-headings>`, :ref:`knoppen <website/themes/button-styles>`, "
"en :ref:`invoervelden <website/themes/input-fields>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:110
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Font Size`: In "
"the :guilabel:`Paragraph`, :guilabel:`Headings`, :guilabel:`Button`, "
"and :guilabel:`Input Fields` sections, use the :guilabel:`Font Size` field "
"to set a default size. Click the :icon:`fa-caret-right` (:guilabel:`Toggle "
"more options`) icon to expand the section and define custom sizes (e.g., "
"based on the heading level, button size, etc.)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Lettergrootte`: Gebruik in de "
"secties :guilabel:`Alinea`, :guilabel:`Koppen`, :guilabel:`Knop`, "
"en :guilabel:`Invoervelden` het veld :guilabel:`Lettergrootte` om een "
"standaardgrootte in te stellen. Klik op het :icon:`fa-caret-right` "
"(:guilabel:`Meer opties in-/uitschakelen`) icoon om de sectie uit te vouwen "
"en aangepaste groottes te definiëren (bv. gebaseerd op het niveau van de "
"kop, knopgrootte, enz.)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:114
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Font Family`: In the :guilabel:`Paragraph`, :guilabel:`Headings`, "
"and :guilabel:`Button` sections, select a font from the dropdown menu."
msgstr ""
